{"tid":1101290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅便臣道寶馬自炒3人傷 撼爆水龍頭噴水","createTime":"2019-04-11T02:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T02:48:16.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9759b2d833f4b1b3ff74bfe18ebbfadf75143e32","tid":1101290,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F2ShNCv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF2ShNCv.png&h=5adc37a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶馬駛至英華女學校對開失控。胡恩宏攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZpJpsCw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpJpsCw.png&h=1f6945f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶馬撞毀消防水龍頭及欄杆。胡恩宏攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkYpsCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkYpsCx.png&h=d8d8d4ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶馬車頭凹陷損毀。胡恩宏攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ChGuDKd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChGuDKd.png&h=15b25350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水龍頭被撞毀噴水。胡恩宏攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vkDkLpe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvkDkLpe.png&h=7f0a361f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶馬撞爛水龍頭，水沿斜路流下。fb突發事故報料區圖片<br />\n<br />\n一輛寶馬房車，早上8時20分左右，沿半山羅便臣道落斜往西環，至英華女學校對開突然失控，猛撞左邊欄杆及消防水龍頭。寶馬車頭凹陷損毀，車內安全氣袋彈出，車上男司機及一男一女乘客受傷，而水龍頭亦被撞毀噴水。救護員接報到場替傷者包紮，其中兩人送院進一步治理。現場交通一度受阻，警方正調查意外原因。"},{"pid":"f0d3609df30f0709a00181d22df27c2617cae4e6","tid":1101290,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:46:04.000Z","msg":"哼！用愛膚堅啦！"},{"pid":"9cc0468ddc4046b2292a012309fb787d9360a3f0","tid":1101290,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"昅旗袍妹昅出事...."},{"pid":"38589a613b5a133b1f2a9b05ee3fd4a6fa127f9f","tid":1101290,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"香港腳發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}